node.text:
@jacobandco Shows building a fully working automotive engine, a one-minute flying tourbillon inclined at a 30-degree angle, and several other components of aesthetic and technical mastery, and placing them inside a tonneau-shaped watch is a horological achievement. The Bugatti Chiron timepiece is a tribute to the hyper sportscar of the same name. It replicates the high-performance automobile, not only in its appearance, but in its fine design and high watchmaking craftsmanship.

After a year of development, @jacobandco and Bugatti created the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon, a watch unlike no other. The tonneau-shaped case of the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron hyper sportscar, giving it a sleek, aerodynamic appearance. Beneath the sapphire crystal is a fully working Bugatti W16 car engine that operates on demand. It's a groundbreaking concept that emulates the speed and beauty of the Chiron. #jacobandco #sapphire

node.text:
The insane Chiron PurSport x The New @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron TourBillon Baguette White Diamonds 💎

The Bugatti Chiron Baguette Rose Gold takes the unique shape and functionality of the Chiron timepiece and adds 355 baguette diamonds and 72 baguette blue sapphires, all invisibly handset. Inside the 18K rose gold case is a fully working replica of the Bugatti “W16" engine clearly visible through sapphire crystal. Activated on demand, the " engine" comes to life with 16 pistons pumping and two turbochargers spinning.

Can anyone guess the price tag on this masterpiece? @jacobandco 🔥 #jacobandco

node.text:
The NEW @jacobandco’s insane Bugatti Chiron Sapphire Crystal 😍🥶

The transparent case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or "engine block," intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for all to see. The case is fully constructed from sapphire crystal which is extremely hard to accomplish. The movement is comprised of 578 components
Mind blowing timepieces 🔥
The @JacobAndCo Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon in the 2 most spectacular and evocative variants. Which one is your favorite? Baguette Rose Gold & Sapphire Crystal. #jacobandco
